1. *Smisla* života je da budemo srećni. (The meaning of life is to be happy.)
2. Ona nema *smisla* za humor. (She has no sense of humor.)
3. Ona nije imala *smisla* da to uradi. (She had no sense to do that.)
4. On je pronašao *smisla* za čitavu priču. (He found the sense for the whole story.)
5. Ovo je izgubilo *smisao*. (This has lost its sense.)